 but a blinding, dazzling, silver animal. He screwed up his eyes, trying to=
 see what it was. It looked like a horse. It was galloping silently away fr=
om him, across the black surface of the lake. He saw it lower its head and =
charge at the swarming dementors... </i>"</span></dd>
