ith <a href=3D"https://harrypotter.fandom.com/wiki/Remus_Lupin" title=3D"Re=
mus Lupin">Remus Lupin</a> in order to learn the advanced charm and was one=
 of the youngest to attempt this charm with actual results.<sup id=3D"cite_=
ref-POA12_1-5" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://harrypotter.fandom.co=
m/wiki/Patronus_Charm#cite_note-POA12-1" aria-label=3D"Reference 1"><span c=
