e=3D"Quidditch">Quidditch</a> match against <a href=3D"https://harrypotter.=
fandom.com/wiki/Ravenclaw" title=3D"Ravenclaw">Ravenclaw</a> in 1994, he ca=
st his very first corporeal Patronus, when several <a href=3D"https://harry=
potter.fandom.com/wiki/Slytherin" title=3D"Slytherin">Slytherin</a> student=
s were impersonating Dementors.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-POA13_9-0" class=3D"refe=
rence"><a href=3D"https://harrypotter.fandom.com/wiki/Patronus_Charm#cite_n=
ote-POA13-9" aria-label=3D"Reference 9"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</spa=
n>9<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> He performed the charm a=
gain in June when he, along with <a href=3D"https://harrypotter.fandom.com/=
wiki/Hermione_Granger" title=3D"Hermione Granger">Hermione Granger</a> and =
<a href=3D"https://harrypotter.fandom.com/wiki/Sirius_Black" title=3D"Siriu=
s Black">Sirius Black</a>, were being attacked by over a hundred <a href=3D=
"https://harrypotter.fandom.com/wiki/Dementor" title=3D"Dementor">Dementors=
</a>, and cast a corporeal Patronus powerful enough to drive them all away.=
<sup id=3D"cite_ref-POA20_10-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://harr=
ypotter.fandom.com/wiki/Patronus_Charm#cite_note-POA20-10" aria-label=3D"Re=
ference 10"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>10<span class=3D"cite-brac=
ket">]</span></a></sup><sup id=3D"cite_ref-POA21_11-0" class=3D"reference">=
<a href=3D"https://harrypotter.fandom.com/wiki/Patronus_Charm#cite_note-POA=
21-11" aria-label=3D"Reference 11"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>11<=
span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
</p><p>On <a href=3D"https://harrypotter.fandom.com/wiki/24_June" title=3D"=
24 June">24 June</a> <a href=3D"https://harrypotter.fandom.com/wiki/1995" t=
itle=3D"1995">1995</a>, Harry cast the charm against a <a href=3D"https://h=
arrypotter.fandom.com/wiki/Triwizard_Maze_Boggart" title=3D"Triwizard Maze =
Boggart">Boggart</a> that he thought was a Dementor during the third task o=
f the <a href=3D"https://harrypotter.fandom.com/wiki/Triwizard_Tournament" =
title=3D"Triwizard Tournament">Triwizard Tournament</a>, in the <a href=3D"=
https://harrypotter.fandom.com/wiki/Triwizard_Maze" title=3D"Triwizard Maze=
">Triwizard Maze</a>.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-GOF31_12-0" class=3D"reference"><a=
 href=3D"https://harrypotter.fandom.com/wiki/Patronus_Charm#cite_note-GOF31=
-12" aria-label=3D"Reference 12"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>12<sp=
an class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> The following summer, he and <=
a href=3D"https://harrypotter.fandom.com/wiki/Dudley_Dursley" title=3D"Dudl=
ey Dursley">Dudley Dursley</a> came under <a href=3D"https://harrypotter.fa=
ndom.com/wiki/Attack_in_Little_Whinging" title=3D"Attack in Little Whinging=
">attack</a> by two <a href=3D"https://harrypotter.fandom.com/wiki/Dementor=
s" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Dementors">Dementors</a> in <a href=3D"ht=
tps://harrypotter.fandom.com/wiki/Little_Whinging" title=3D"Little Whinging=
">Little Whinging</a>, and Harry managed to drive them away with the charm,=
<sup id=3D"cite_ref-OOTP1_13-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://harr=
ypotter.fandom.com/wiki/Patronus_Charm#cite_note-OOTP1-13" aria-label=3D"Re=
ference 13"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>13<span class=3D"cite-brac=
ket">]</span></a></sup> leading to him being put on <a href=3D"https://harr=
ypotter.fandom.com/wiki/Disciplinary_hearing_of_Harry_Potter" title=3D"Disc=
iplinary hearing of Harry Potter">trial</a> for <a href=3D"https://harrypot=
ter.fandom.com/wiki/Underage_magic" title=3D"Underage magic">underage magic=
