et">]</span></span></h2>
<p>A successfully conjured Patronus could take one of two forms: incorporea=
l and corporeal. Both types varied greatly in their appearances and strengt=
h.
</p>
<h3><span class=3D"mw-headline" id=3D"Incorporeal">Incorporeal</span><span =
class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><sp=
an class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<div class=3D"quote">
<dl><dd><span title=3D"Source:&nbsp;Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaba=
n">"<i>A thin wisp of silver escaped his wand and hovered like mist before =
him.</i>"</span></dd>
<dd>=E2=80=94 Description of Harry Potter's incorporeal shield Patronus<sup=
 class=3D"noprint"><a href=3D"https://harrypotter.fandom.com/wiki/Harry_Pot=
